  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "There's a lot of trouble in the\nvicinity of the Great Northern\nbridge in the west end of town on\naccount of a hobo camp and the\ndepredations its members commit\nagainst chicken roosts. Several\npeople have missed chickens that\nfail to answer roll call at feeding\ntime. The climax was capped yes\nterday when a dozen fine chickens\nbelonging to Mrs. Rowell were\nstolen. Sh notified the police and\nofficers went to the vicinity, but\nthe hobo camp was found de-\nserted."
    }
